Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}財閥舉辦從古至今傳承的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從沒有被公諸於世的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}慘絕人寰的賭博比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}女高中生得手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是中大獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剝光她 剝光她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.19,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這女的巨乳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼會變成這樣 為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.28,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 野本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}往秩父方向開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}隨便玩玩以後就扔了這女的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那個啊 北條
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我聽說是去搭訕才跟著你們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是犯罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還是別…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.42,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你害怕個鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也是共犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}過會也讓你來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正你肯定是處男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再怎麼喊也不會有人來救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我果然要停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒時間解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照我說的開車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快點 回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.00,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}北條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道哪個是北條…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但所有人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 快開車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果你不想和他們一起死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你最好別看簾子後面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又不能開車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還嘔吐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是個派不上用場的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別想著逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生 我是瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是 我到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}遇到了點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是 那個混蛋也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.22,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這…這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只有這裡像場地一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是摔跤台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是某個財閥的私有土地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聚集著無處可去的東西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大型垃圾啊屍體之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有我們這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請…請…請救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我完全不知道發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}女高中生在車裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把朋友大卸八塊堆成了血海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那恐怕是獸人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 獸人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同時具備人類的大腦和野獸的牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}擁有遠遠凌駕於人類之上的力量的新人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 現在不是說這種蠢話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你剛剛說了蠢這個字嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}區區一個沒有力量又矮小的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟敢對著百獸之王的獸鬪士獅子說蠢這個字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是不想活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我掂掂自己的斤兩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是想幫你處理掉垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他還有用處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聽祠堂說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和我之間的賭率是100比0
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照這樣下去的話「牙鬪」就無法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}牙…斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}的確是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}身經百戰的我和今天才第一次戰鬥的你之間的勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.95,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以就讓這傢伙下賭注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}賭1000萬我贏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣賭率就變成99比1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那傢伙付的出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}讓他用身體付就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}脊髓 內臟 眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他還很年輕所以能賣得很貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你別擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.72,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你覺得你還逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}光是我現在沒馬上殺掉你這一點你就該心存感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「牙鬪」到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}現在開始我在這和那傢伙打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我贏了的話你就會得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我輸了的話你就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}死 但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對手是那樣的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}與性別和體格的差距無關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獠牙更鋒利者獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是「牙鬪」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(621.333,468.733)\fad(300,0)}第一牙 獠牙更鋒利者獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個女孩也是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聽說你還從未輸過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}王中之王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是誇張的綽號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然在挑釁他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是有打倒那傢伙的自信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也想要個那樣的稱號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你覺得「雷歐殺手」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正最後贏的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即便對手只是一隻小白兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也要用盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是我雷歐的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這女孩要被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我得快點去求救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這…這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的身體居然動不了
Comment: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（獅子咆哮）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「雷歐獅吼」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獅子的咆哮聲在貓科動物中是最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能夠威懾所有動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使它們動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}膽敢挑戰王的愚蠢與恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就由你的身體好好記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我雷歐獅吼之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你應該會因為本能的恐懼不能動彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐懼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐懼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從我出生開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的字典裡就沒有恐懼兩個字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所有的動物都會恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}報上名來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獸鬪士 蜜獾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,獸鬪士蜜獾
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宇崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野性和暴力的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}面對獅子等大型動物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾也會毫不畏懼地與其戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被認為是世界上最強悍不怕死的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}收入金氏世界紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}換言之蜜獾是世界小型哺乳動物的最強者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}至少給我記住對手的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蠢貨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然對我說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這小崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我把話收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「蜜獾斬」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜獾斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷歐竟然是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勝率可是99比1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}您看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是我的最高傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獸鬪士 蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被你擺了一手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一個人贏得了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是個是挺有趣的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如你所願殺了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這個強姦犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全部都是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別在我耳邊大吼大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小心我殺了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來不是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼 完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}得救了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.45,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放開我 殺了你喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看你傷得這麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}趕快去治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是留下傷疤的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個時間不知道還有醫院開門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說我們究竟在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這點傷一會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.84,Default - up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可是女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我馬上就把他處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊? 這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之後不知為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我把她帶到我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說自己的傷不能去一般的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是簡單包紮之後就睡一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天真是非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那件事我不會對任何人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用你說我也會走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你加得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我差不多該去大學了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給我安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把嘴閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不准呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣看簡直就像普通的女孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你已經做得很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難道不是嗎 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是比試前出了那種差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本打算一擊擊倒雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結果卻拖到中盤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}害得祠堂先生為我擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從未感受到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說這又是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祠堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次見面 我是祠堂零一 是瞳的監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}監護人 看起來不像是父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次見面 我是….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本裕也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高麗川大學經濟學院經濟專業大二學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學號E4291
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}籍貫長野 現居住於大學附近的公寓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}柳澤公寓201號房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被摸根摸底的調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說起來你覺得怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在特等席上觀看「牙鬪」的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是…昨天的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒錯 獸人之間的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}透過最新的基因強化手術 獲得野獸能力的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}外形和常人沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但獸化之後就這會變異進入戰鬥形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼會… 有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你對財閥有所了解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}延續400年 世界上最古老的富商一族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是財閥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然在戰後被解體了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而當今日本的經濟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}八菱 三門 石田 角供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也正處於這四個財閥的支配之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}財閥們賭上各自的發言權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}進行非公開的代理戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是「牙鬪」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}每個時代被稱之為最強的人們互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而近年 「牙鬪」的戰鬥者全部都換成了獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們管理局的工作就是為了使「牙鬪」更加順利的進行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}關於昨晚你朋友們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我們已經視作交通事故死處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對…對不起 我真的不知道目的會是性侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我和北條他們只不過是以前打短工時認識的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他們突然聯繫我 說要去搭訕 叫我來當司機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這小子 少在這裡裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在駕駛室裡一臉想幹的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我本想阻止他們的 請相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鬼才信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的話 我也能安心的把瞳交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}讓瞳來做你的貼身保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不要呢 為什麼我要保護這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他現在是 獸鬪士中唯一的出資者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是他發生了什麼閃失 你也會失去「牙鬪」的參賽資格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}變成這樣的話 我方也會損失巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希望你能協助我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果能幫上祠堂先生的忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}野本 也請你在下一場的比賽中出資
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}費用方面 請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是這次分紅的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}具體的時間 之後會再給出指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是意外呢 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟然真是個普通學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是既然這樣 我們來管理那筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把他拘束起來不更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒必要讓瞳去保護他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是必要的環節
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說不定那樣的年輕人 意外的能補充瞳所欠缺的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管怎麼說 下次的「牙鬪」會是一場血雨腥風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}9998 9999
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然有一億元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你數多少次都不會變的 真是閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也差不多該去學校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 拿著這麼大筆錢才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說你不也是高中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暫時休學中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且不知道是託誰的福 制服都成碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\frz351.7\pos(470.4,530.6)}內衣 \N牙刷 \N杯子\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\pos(404.8,549.8)}水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\pos(406.4,612.2)}漫畫雜誌HEROS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn方正喵鸣\c&H00545757\fs30\b1\frz353.8\pos(313.6,653.8)}趕緊去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你馬上去買回來 還有甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你自己去買怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}殺了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快去 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 真傷腦筋 被捲進這麼麻煩的事裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過仔細想想 這不是在和女子高中生同居嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好意思 稍微有東西想讓你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就…就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 等等 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}更近一點 請靠近好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然讓你看見了 就不能簡單放你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把你知道關於蜜獾的事全部說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}關於我的事 來問我怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我正好就在這附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來 開始吧 「牙鬪」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,第一集 指引我吧 小押繪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}指引我吧 小押繪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明聽說家店的鬆餅很好吃才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這些客人都是什麼人啊 我都不好意思進去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}砂糖鬆餅蜂蜜特別版兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個人 連我的份都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蜜獾 以及黑喉響蜜鴷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通過最喜歡的蜂蜜 維持著共生關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這兩隻動物的相遇 是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}話說 你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過 小押繪才不是什麼獸人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}定期報告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對於把王者獅子打倒的蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}各個財閥都圍繞她開始謀劃策略
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}假如 目標瞄準的是野本的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}無法預測瞳是否會去保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(621.333,468.733)\fad(00,0)}第二牙 糟糕 要迷上了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一集「糟糕 要迷上了」 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.74,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混ざり合う叫びは静寂を切り裂く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.54,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}研ぎ澄ませる野生で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.37,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}勝者だけが繋ぐ明日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く磨いた牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.00,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}噛み付くその狂気
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.17,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}立ち向かおうか？戦いにわけなどいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}強さ求めるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:06.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋に繋がれた生命の約束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}止まらない進化が呼び覚ましてく　命の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:17.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}狂おしく飢えて　乾いた心だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:25.17,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}溢れる狂気も纏って　今立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}Shout and roar！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:31.13,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}解き放つ咆哮　その闇を震わす
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.93,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}恐れなく踏み出した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.64,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}その一歩が痛みを呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.52,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}鋭く刺さる罪は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.31,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}この世界に潜む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.48,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真実はその嘘を飲み込んだままで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}全てを見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:32.74,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}混雜交織的叫喊打破寂靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.54,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}敏感的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯有勝者擁有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}打磨出鋒利的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.00,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}緊咬不放的瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:48.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}去迎敵嗎？戰鬥不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}唯獨追求強大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:06.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}螺旋維繫的生命的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}無止境的進化喚起生命的顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:17.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}瘋狂地渴望 只剩乾枯的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:25.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}滿溢的瘋狂纏身 現在站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}叫喊和咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:31.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}被解放的咆哮 使黑暗顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}無所畏懼的邁出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.64,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}哪怕這一步會招致疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}銳利地刺入的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}潛伏在這個世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:46.48,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}真實吞嚥下這份謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.61,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur8}卻注視著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲望のままにあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どうにでもなれなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}可愛いもの見たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.10,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}近づいちゃ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.64,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}儚げな笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.02,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}水色の涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.52,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}カムフラージュ切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.15,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}危ないその匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.05,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}か弱いフリの牙に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:49.01,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}噛み付かれないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:55.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あの子はどこから見ても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:58.60,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ケダモノダモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}遵循本能的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}變成怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}對可愛事物充滿好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:16.10,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}但卻不可以靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.64,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是夢幻的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.02,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是淡藍色的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.52,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都無法掩蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.15,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這危險的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要當心別被
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:49.01,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這看似弱小的獠牙緊咬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:55.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不論從哪個角度看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:58.60,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}那個孩子都是鄙劣的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
